    elementType: text
    bounds: [700, 134, 192, 16]
    content: {fontSize: 9.5, color: "$ink", bold: true, letterSpacing: 1, align: [left, middle], wrap: false, text: "11+ VIEWS GERADAS"}
  - elementId: views-list
    elementType: text
    bounds: [700, 154, 194, 264]
    content:
      fontSize: 8.5
      color: "$body"
      lineHeight: 1.42
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong>.mavis/learning_state.yaml</strong> → planner Mavis (estados em PT)</p>
        <p style="margin-top:4px"><strong>whiteboard/profile.yaml · learner_profile.md · trail.md</strong> → minimaxDojo</p>
        <p style="margin-top:4px"><strong>learner.ts · projects.ts · agents.ts · cycle.ts</strong> → dashboard codexDojo</p>
        <p style="margin-top:4px"><strong>learner.ts</strong> → codexdojo-os (projeção própria, mesmo snapshot)</p>
        <p style="margin-top:4px"><strong>reviewSlice.ts</strong> → pixel-quest</p>
        <p style="margin-top:4px"><strong>reviewSlice.ts × 16</strong> → voxelDojo (fan-out game-*)</p>
        <p style="margin-top:4px"><strong>BACKLOG_STATUS.md</strong> → curriculum/</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px"><span style="color:$muted;">Todo arquivo gerado traz o cabeçalho "AUTO-GENERATED … DO NOT EDIT BY HAND".</span></p>
  - elementId: rules-head
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 404, 608, 16]
    content: {fontSize: 10.5, color: "$ink", bold: true, letterSpacing: 1.2, align: [left, middle], wrap: false, text: "REGRAS DE ORDENAÇÃO (substrate/interface.md)"}
  - elementId: rules
    elementType: text
    bounds: [56, 426, 608, 66]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 10.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>1 · Sempre edite a <strong>fonte canônica</strong> primeiro; depois chame <strong>sync()</strong>.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:5px">2 · <strong>Nunca</strong> escreva numa view derivada nem faça back-port de mudanças para o canônico.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:5px">3 · O dumper YAML evita anchors/aliases: o arquivo canônico permanece "plain and greppable".</p>
  - elementId: footer-line
